{
  "page": "Walder",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Walder</b> is a given name common among the members and descendants of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a>. According to Lord Walder Frey, his descendants name children after him hoping that the head of their house will favor them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a>, Lord of the Crossing</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey_(son_of_Jammos)\" title=\"Walder Frey (son of Jammos)\">Walder Frey</a>, also known as <i>Big Walder</i>, eldest son of Ser Jammos Frey and Sallei Paege</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey_(son_of_Ryman)\" title=\"Walder Frey (son of Ryman)\">Walder Frey</a>, also known as <i>Black Walder</i>, second son of Ser Ryman Frey</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey_(son_of_Merrett)\" title=\"Walder Frey (son of Merrett)\">Walder Frey</a>, also known as <i>Little Walder</i>, only son of Merrett Frey and Mariya Darry</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey_(son_of_Emmon)\" title=\"Walder Frey (son of Emmon)\">Walder Frey</a>, also known as <i>Red Walder</i>, fourth son of Ser Emmon Frey and Genna Lannister</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Brax\" title=\"Walder Brax\">Walder Brax</a>, second son of Lady Morya Frey and Ser Flement Brax</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Goodbrook\" title=\"Walder Goodbrook\">Walder Goodbrook</a>, only son of Kyra Frey and Ser Garse Goodbrook</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Haigh\" title=\"Walder Haigh\">Walder Haigh</a>, only son of Ser Harys Haigh, eldest son of Perriane Frey</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Rivers\" title=\"Walder Rivers\">Walder Rivers</a>, eldest bastard son of Lord Walder Frey</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Vance\" title=\"Walder Vance\">Walder Vance</a>, eldest son of Maegelle Frey and Ser Dafyn Vance</li></ul>\n<p>Of no known relation to House Frey:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Hodor\" title=\"Hodor\">Walder</a>, the birth name of Hodor, a stableboy at <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_of_Woodmere\" title=\"Walder of Woodmere\">Walder of Woodmere</a>, a knight from Woodmere during the reign of King Daeron II Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Stackspear\" title=\"Walder Stackspear\">Walder Stackspear</a>, a knight of House Stackspear during the reign of King Daeron II Targaryen</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walder&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey\" title=\"Walda Frey\">Walda Frey</a> (disambiguation)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Rivers_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Walda Rivers (disambiguation)\">Walda Rivers (disambiguation)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walderan_Tarbeck\" title=\"Walderan Tarbeck\">Walderan Tarbeck</a>, the last confirmed Lord of Tarbeck Hall and head of House Tarbeck</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walton_Frey\" title=\"Walton Frey\">Walton Frey</a>, third son of Ser Stevron Frey</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Waltyr_Frey\" title=\"Waltyr Frey\">Waltyr Frey</a>, third son of Lord Walder Frey and his seventh wife, Annara Farring</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walder&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_59\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 59\">Chapter 59</a>, Catelyn IX.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404194534\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.010 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 81/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 423/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 526/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.353      1 -total\n 74.43%    3.984      1 Template:Ref\n 43.38%    2.322      1 Template:Ref/core\n 24.02%    1.286      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:17429-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404194534 and revision id 323472\n -->\n",
